title: Skyrim25
description: Skyrim as Todd intended. The bare minimum to make vanilla Skyrim playable in 2025 as it should have been at launch in 2011. A clean "vanilla-ish" base to build upon or just to play as-is. Some bugs are fixed, while others are kept intact, like the infamous fortify restoration loop - because bugs are part of the fun. Featuring cleaned textures for a slightly improved look, plus untouched vanilla gameplay and zero content mods. Featuring full CC and plain old Special Edition profiles.
author: Fauxvale
